    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase the curtailment period when Tier 2 Visa holders lose their jobs",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "People on Tier 2 work visas depend on their continued employment to remain in the UK. If for anyone reason they lose their jobs, as is happening to many due to the economic downturn, they have 60 days to make a new visa application or leave the country. This isn't enough time. We want it increased.",
